## Enforcement

**Before starting ANY phase:**

- [ ] Phase folder created in `docs/phases/` or `phases/`
- [ ] README.md with objectives and success criteria
- [ ] planning.md with approach and tasks
- [ ] PHASE_STATUS.md updated

**During phase implementation:**

- [ ] implementation.md updated regularly
- [ ] Progress tracked in README.md
- [ ] Decisions documented

**Before marking phase complete:**

- [ ] testing.md with all test results
- [ ] completion.md with summary
- [ ] PHASE_STATUS.md shows completion
- [ ] All success criteria met

